        Ceramics by Lisa Larson-Walker/ProPublica, video by Lisa Larson-Walker/ProPublica, Gerardo del Valle/ProPublica and Katie Campbell/ProPublica
    </span>
    
    
    </figcaption>

        </figure>


    
    <div class="opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper  opener__text-start--2 opener__text-width--4 opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper--valign-center opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper--mobile-fullbleed">

                    <span class="opener__topics  opener__topics--vertical-rule opener__topics--dark">
            <a class="opener__topics-link  opener__topics-link--dark" href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/health-care">Health Care</a>
        </span>
    
    <h1 class="opener__hed  opener__hed--vertical-rule opener__hed--dark" >        The Price of Remission
    </h1>

    
            <div class="article-meta-1  article-meta-1--dark">
            <span class="article-meta-1__byline">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/david-armstrong">David Armstrong</a>            </span>
            <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-05-08EDT05:00">May 8, 2025, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
            </time>
        </div>
    
    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

            <div class="content"> <!-- not sure if this is the best way to reestablish the text column -->
            <h2 class="opener__dek opener__dek--match-text-column" >                When I was diagnosed with cancer, I set out to understand why a single pill of Revlimid cost the same as a new iPhone. I’ve covered high drug prices as a reporter for years. What I discovered shocked even me.
            </h2>
        </div>
    
</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--center      article-meta-1--hide-byline " data-pp-location="article meta">

    <span class="article-meta-1__byline" data-pp-location="article byine">
        by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/david-armstrong">David Armstrong</a>    </span>
    <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
        <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-05-08EDT05:00">May 8, 2025, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
    </time>

    <div class="article-meta-1__section-actions
         article-meta-1__section-actions--center     " data-pp-location="article story-tools">
