<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="55.0">When she returned two weeks later, her mailbox was full of lab results for Jimmy. He was still alive. She sat down to double-check the results, which showed declining amounts of a cancer marker. “For 30 minutes, I was the only person in the world who knew this worked,” she said.</p>
        
    
                    
<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="56.0">Singhal walked down to Barlogie’s office to give him the news. “He took me by the hand, opened a window and shouted, ‘Thank you, God,’” she said.</p>
        
    
                    

<figure
    data-pp-id="57"
    data-pp-blocktype="image"
    class="bb-image full center  wide-sm wrap 
                ">

    


            
    


