    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/noaa-michigan-lab-toxic-algae-blooms-great-lakes-drinking-water">
                                    Millions of People Depend on the Great Lakes’ Water Supply. Trump Decimated the Lab Protecting It.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            The Trump administration’s slashing of budgets and staff have Great Lakes scientists concerned that they have lost the ability to protect the public from toxic algal blooms, which can kill animals and sicken people.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
                        <span class="story-card__byline-author">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/anna-clark">Anna Clark</a>,
            </span>
                        <span class="story-card__byline-dateline">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-05-06EDT06:00">May 6, 2025, 6 a.m. EDT</time>
            </span>
        </p>

